article_id:1345,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Raid Event, Timeworn Torment, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/13d17ab68fec1dce084e9b77ca345541.png,message:<div>The Timeworn Torment raid event will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590559200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>During this event, you can use co-op play to fight against the shadow-attuned raid boss.</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/13d17ab68fec1dce084e9b77ca345541.png"></div><div>One day, some time after the prince and friends sealed Qitian Dasheng away along with the Qilin relic Jin Gu Er, Xuan Zang&#39;s apprentice Wu Kong arrived at the Halidom. As it turns out, the seal was broken, but when the prince and friends went to survey the situation, they met the kind fiend Mei Hou Wang. Now the convictions of those who seek to defeat Mei Hou Wang and those who seek to protect him will clash!</div><div>Note: &nbsp;Certain part of the text has been corrected.<br><br>Event theme song: &quot;Force Your Way&quot; by Takayoshi Tanimoto<br><br>â– Notes<br>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in event quests.<br>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1590472800,update_time1590653795